a.communication_channel_value else null end as email_addr,     CASE WHEN a.communication_channel_type_code = 'phone' then a.communication_channel_value else null end as primary_phone,     CASE WHEN communication_channel_active_status_code = '1_year_active' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS active_1yr_flag,     CASE WHEN communication_channel_active_status_code = '2_year_active' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS active_2yr_flag,     CASE WHEN communication_channel_active_status_code = '3_year_active' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS active_3yr_flag,     CASE WHEN communication_channel_active_status_code = '4_year_active' DATEDIFF(YEAR, b.birth_date, CURRENT_DATE) BETWEEN 0 AND 2 THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END AS children_age_0_2,     CASE WHEN DATEDIFF(YEAR, b.birth_date, CURRENT_DATE) BETWEEN 3 AND 5 THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END AS children_age_3_5,     CASE WHEN DATEDIFF(YEAR, b.birth_date, CURRENT_DATE) BETWEEN 6 AND 10 THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END AS children_age_6_10,     CASE WHEN DATEDIFF(YEAR, b.birth_date, CURRENT_DATE) BETWEEN 22000) and (current_date - 10000) or date_of_birth is null) and (est_income in ('$50,000 - $74,999', '$75,000 - $99,999', '$100,000 - $124,999', 'Greater than $124,999')  or est_net_worth not in ('Less than $1', '$1 - $4,999', '$5,000 - $9,999', '$10,000 - $24,999', '$25,000 - $49,999') or discretionary_income_index_cd > 100) )

WITH age_groups AS (     SELECT          INDIVIDUAL_ID,         CASE    WHEN DATE_DIFF('year', TO_DATE(birth_date, 'YYYY-MM-DD'), CURRENT_DATE) BETWEEN 18 AND 24 THEN '18-24'             WHEN DATE_DIFF('year', TO_DATE(birth_date, 'YYYY-MM-DD'), CURRENT_DATE) BETWEEN 25 AND 34 THEN '25-34'             WHEN DATE_DIFF('year', TO_DATE(birth_date, 'YYYY-MM-DD'), CURRENT_DATE) BETWEEN 35 AND 44 THEN '35-44'             WHEN DATE_DIFF('year', TO_DATE(birth_date, 'YYYY-MM-DD'), CURRENT_DATE) BETWEEN 45 AND 54 THEN '45-54'             WHEN DATE_DIFF('year', TO_DATE(birth_date, 'YYYY-MM-DD'), CURRENT_DATE) BETWEEN 55 AND 64 THEN '55-64'             ELSE '65+'         END AS age_group     FROM fulfillment_ptc.ptc_fan_uvof_plus     WHERE birth_date IS NOT NULL     AND favorite_team_individual = 'sea'  ) SELECT      age_group,     COUNT(INDIVIDUAL_ID) * 100.0 / SUM(COUNT(INDIVIDUAL_ID)) OVER () AS pct_of_total FROM age_groups GROUP BY age_group ORDER BY age_group;

eps_crtd_dt,     c.latest_activity_source_system_id as eps_lst_upd_by_run,     c.latest_activity_date as eps_lst_upd_dt,     d.favorite_team_individual as fav_team_club_cd,     b.first_name as first_nm,  b.first_name_hash_value as firstname,     b.last_name as last_nm,      b.last_name_hash_value as surname,     b.gender_code as gender,     a.is_league_shop_flag as isshop,     a.item_id,     a.product_size_code as item_size,     a.total_discount_amount as order_discount_total,     a.transaction_timestamp as order_date, a.order_id,     a.total_transaction_amount as order_net_total,     a.order_promotion_code as order_promo,     a.total_shipping_cost_amount as order_ship_total,     a.total_tax_amount as order_tax_total,     a.player_name,     a.product_category_code as prod_category, shipping.state_code as ship_address_state,     shipping.zip_code as ship_address_zip_cd, a.source_site_id as site_id,     a.team_name as team,     a.unit_price_amount as unit_price FROM fulfillment_ptc.ptc_fan_merchandise_transaction_detail a LEFT JOIN fulfillment_ptc.ptc_fan_individual_profile b  ON b.individual_id = a.individual_id LEFT JOIN fulfillment_ptc.ptc_fan_communication_channel_profile c  ON c.individual_id = a.individual_id      AND c.communication_channel_hash_value = a.communication_channel_hash_value LEFT JOIN (select individual_id, communication_channel_hash_value, max(address_line_1) as address_line_1, max(address_line_2) as address_line_2, max(city_name) as city_name, max(country_code) as country_code, max(state_code) as state_code, max(zip_code) as zip_code         from fulfillment_ptc.ptc_fan_address_details         where address_type_code = 'billing'         group by 1, 2) billing ON billing.individual_id = a.individual_id  AND billing.communication_channel_hash_value = a.communication_channel_hash_value  LEFT JOIN (select individual_id, communication_channel_hash_value, max(address_line_1) as address_line_1, max(address_line_2) as address_line_2, max(city_name) as city_name, max(country_code) as country_code, max(state_code) as state_code, max(zip_code) as zip_code         from fulfillment_ptc.ptc_fan_address_details         where address_type_code = 'mailing'         group by 1, 2) shipping ON shipping.individual_id = a.individual_id  AND shipping.communication_channel_hash_value = a.communication_channel_hash_value  LEFT JOIN fulfillment_ptc.ptc_fan_uvof_plus d  ON d.individual_id = a.individual_id  AND d.communication_channel_hash_value = a.communication_channel_hash_value where bill_address_country != 'usa' or ship_address_country !='usa' order by  order_date desc, order_id

WITH total_counts AS (     SELECT          SUM(COUNT(DISTINCT a.individual_id)) OVER () AS total_fans,         SUM(COUNT(DISTINCT a.profile_id)) OVER () AS total_fan_profiles     FROM          fulfillment_ptc.ptc_fan_source_profile a         INNER JOIN fulfillment_ptc.ptc_fan_uvof_plus b ON a.individual_id = b.individual_id         AND b.birth_date IS NOT NULL         AND b.favorite_team_individual = 'sea'     WHERE          a.age < 30 ) SELECT      a.profile_source_system_name,     AVG(a.age) AS average_age,     COUNT(DISTINCT a.individual_id) AS fans,     COUNT(DISTINCT a.profile_id) AS fan_profiles,     COUNT(DISTINCT a.individual_id) * 1.0 / (SELECT total_fans FROM total_counts) AS fans_percentage,     COUNT(DISTINCT a.profile_id) * 1.0 / (SELECT total_fan_profiles FROM total_counts) AS fan_profiles_percentage FROM      fulfillment_ptc.ptc_fan_source_profile a     INNER JOIN fulfillment_ptc.ptc_fan_uvof_plus b ON a.individual_id = b.individual_id     AND b.birth_date IS NOT NULL     AND b.favorite_team_individual = 'sea' WHERE      a.age < 30 GROUP BY      a.profile_source_system_name ORDER BY      COUNT(DISTINCT a.individual_id) DESC;

WITH numbers AS (     SELECT generate_series(0, 1439) AS n   ), dates AS (     SELECT generate_series('2025-01-01'::TIMESTAMP, CURRENT_DATE::TIMESTAMP, INTERVAL '1 day') AS day_series ) SELECT      day_series + (n * INTERVAL '1 minute') AS interval_time FROM numbers CROSS JOIN dates ORDER BY interval_time

WITH numbers AS (     SELECT (ROW_NUMBER() OVER ()) - 1 AS n     FROM pg_catalog.pg_class a     JOIN pg_catalog.pg_class b ON 1=1     LIMIT 1440   ), dates AS (     SELECT CAST('2025-01-01' AS TIMESTAMP) + (INTERVAL '1 day' * (ROW_NUMBER() OVER () - 1)) AS day_series     FROM pg_catalog.pg_class     LIMIT (CURRENT_DATE - '2025-01-01') + 1   ) SELECT      day_series + (n * INTERVAL '1 minute') AS interval_time FROM numbers CROSS JOIN dates ORDER BY interval_time

WITH RECURSIVE dates(target) AS (     SELECT CAST('2025-01-01' AS TIMESTAMP)     UNION ALL     SELECT target + INTERVAL '1 day'     FROM dates     WHERE target + INTERVAL '1 day' <= CURRENT_DATE ) SELECT     target + (n * INTERVAL '1 minute') AS interval_time FROM (     SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER () - 1 AS n     FROM pg_catalog.pg_class a     JOIN pg_catalog.pg_class b ON 1=1     LIMIT 1440 ) numbers CROSS JOIN dates ORDER BY interval_time;

 billing.city_name as bill_address_city,     billing.country_code as bill_address_country,     billing.state_code as bill_address_state,     billing.zip_code as bill_address_zip_cd, SELECT   COUNT(*) AS total_records,   COUNT(DISTINCT transaction_id) AS distinct_transactions,   COUNT(DISTINCT account_id) AS distinct_accounts,   COUNT(DISTINCT event_id) AS distinct_events,   COUNT(DISTINCT venue_id) AS distinct_venues,   COUNT(DISTINCT club_code) AS distinct_clubs,   AVG(gross_transactional_value_amount) AS avg_transaction_value   /* Financial metrics */,   SUM(gross_transactional_value_amount::float) AS total_transaction_value,   AVG(ticket_revenue_amount::float) AS avg_ticket_revenue,   SUM(ticket_revenue_amount::float) AS total_ticket_revenue,   AVG(buyer_fee_amount::float) AS avg_buyer_fee,   AVG(seller_fee_amount::float) AS avg_seller_fee,   AVG(retail_fee_amount::float) AS avg_retail_fee,   AVG(days_between_transaction_and_event::float) AS avg_days_to_event   /* Timing metrics */,   AVG(days_listing_before_purchase::float) AS avg_days_listed,   AVG(minutes_listing_before_purchase::float) AS avg_minutes_listed,   AVG(listing_price_amount::float) AS avg_listing_price   /* Price metrics */,   AVG(original_listing_price_amount::float) AS avg_original_price,   COUNT(DISTINCT event_type_code) AS distinct_event_types   /* Event statistics */,   COUNT(DISTINCT season_type_code) AS distinct_season_types,   MIN(season_year) AS earliest_season,   MAX(season_year) AS latest_season,   SUM(     CASE       WHEN game_attendance_flag ILIKE '%Y%' THEN 1       ELSE 0     END   ) AS total_attended   /* Attendance and complimentary tickets */,   SUM(     CASE       WHEN total_complimented_flag ILIKE '%Y%' THEN 1       ELSE 0     END   ) AS total_complimentary_tickets,   COUNT(DISTINCT venue_city) AS distinct_cities   /* Venue metrics */,   COUNT(DISTINCT stadium_level_code) AS distinct_stadium_levels,   COUNT(DISTINCT section_name) AS distinct_sections,   MIN(transaction_timestamp) AS earliest_transaction   /* Transaction timing */,   MAX(transaction_timestamp) AS latest_transaction,   MIN(event_start_date) AS earliest_event   /* Event timing */,   MAX(event_start_date) AS latest_event,   COUNT(DISTINCT market_place_code) AS distinct_marketplaces   /* Market metrics */,   COUNT(DISTINCT sale_type_code) AS distinct_sale_types,   COUNT(DISTINCT primary_purchase_type_code) AS distinct_purchase_types,   COUNT(DISTINCT seat_class_code) AS distinct_seat_classes   /* Seat metrics */,   COUNT(DISTINCT price_level) AS distinct_price_levels,   COUNT(DISTINCT seat_status_code) AS distinct_seat_statuses FROM   fulfillment_ptc.ptc_fan_ticket_transaction_details;

SELECT a.individual_id,  a.communication_channel_hash_value, a.merchandise_source_system_id as address_source, billing.address_line_1 as bill_address_1,  billing.address_line_2 as bill_address_2,  billing.city_name as bill_address_city,     billing.country_code as bill_address_country,     billing.state_code as bill_address_state,     billing.zip_code as bill_address_zip_cd, CASE WHEN c.communication_channel_type_code = 'email' THEN c.communication_channel_value ELSE NULL END AS email_addr, CASE WHEN c.league_contactability_status_code = 'cnfrmd' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS email_opt_in,     a.source_record_created_timestamp as eps_crtd_by_run_id,     a.record_created_timestamp as eps_crtd_dt,     c.latest_activity_source_system_id as eps_lst_upd_by_run,     c.latest_activity_date as eps_lst_upd_dt,     d.favorite_team_individual as fav_team_club_cd,     b.first_name as first_nm,  b.first_name_hash_value as firstname,     b.last_name as last_nm,      b.last_name_hash_value as surname,     b.gender_code as gender,     a.is_league_shop_flag as isshop,     a.item_id,     a.product_size_code as item_size,     a.total_discount_amount as order_discount_total,     a.transaction_timestamp as order_dt, a.order_id,     a.total_transaction_amount_excluding_tax as order_gross_subtotal,     a.total_transaction_amount as order_net_total,     a.order_promotion_code as order_promo,     a.total_shipping_cost_amount as order_ship_total,     a.total_tax_amount as order_tax_total,     a.player_name,     a.product_category_code as prod_category,     a.product_id as prod_id,     a.product_name as prod_nm,     a.product_sub_class_code as prod_sub_class,     a.product_sub_category_code as prod_subcategory,     a.item_sold_quantity as qty_sold,     a.item_discount_total as item_disc_total,     a.discount_amount as item_disc_total_2,  shipping.address_line_1 as ship_address_1,  shipping.address_line_2 as ship_address_2,  shipping.city_name as ship_address_city,     shipping.country_code as ship_address_country,     shipping.state_code as ship_address_state,     shipping.zip_code as ship_address_zip_cd, a.source_site_id as site_id,     a.team_name as team,     a.unit_price_amount as unit_price FROM fulfillment_ptc.ptc_fan_merchandise_transaction_detail a LEFT JOIN fulfillment_ptc.ptc_fan_individual_profile b  ON b.individual_id = a.individual_id LEFT JOIN fulfillment_ptc.ptc_fan_communication_channel_profile c  ON c.individual_id = a.individual_id      AND c.communication_channel_hash_value = a.communication_channel_hash_value LEFT JOIN (select individual_id, communication_channel_hash_value, max(address_line_1) as address_line_1, max(address_line_2) as address_line_2, max(city_name) as city_name, max(country_code) as country_code, max(state_code) as state_code, max(zip_code) as zip_code         from fulfillment_ptc.ptc_fan_address_details         where address_type_code = 'billing'         group by 1, 2) billing ON billing.individual_id = a.individual_id  AND billing.communication_channel_hash_value = a.communication_channel_hash_value  LEFT JOIN (select individual_id, communication_channel_hash_value, max(address_line_1) as address_line_1, max(address_line_2) as address_line_2, max(city_name) as city_name, max(country_code) as country_code, max(state_code) as state_code, max(zip_code) as zip_code         from fulfillment_ptc.ptc_fan_address_details         where address_type_code = 'mailing'         group by 1, 2) shipping ON shipping.individual_id = a.individual_id  AND shipping.communication_channel_hash_value = a.communication_channel_hash_value  LEFT JOIN fulfillment_ptc.ptc_fan_uvof_plus d  ON d.individual_id = a.individual_id  AND d.communication_channel_hash_value = a.communication_channel_hash_value     limit 10 ;

SELECT   COUNT(*) AS total_records,   COUNT(DISTINCT transaction_id) AS distinct_transactions,   COUNT(DISTINCT account_id) AS distinct_accounts,   COUNT(DISTINCT event_id) AS distinct_events,   COUNT(DISTINCT venue_id) AS distinct_venues,   COUNT(DISTINCT club_code) AS distinct_clubs,   AVG(gross_transactional_value_amount) AS avg_transaction_value   /* Financial metrics */,   SUM(gross_transactional_value_amount::float) AS total_transaction_value,   AVG(ticket_revenue_amount::float) AS avg_ticket_revenue,   SUM(ticket_revenue_amount::float) AS total_ticket_revenue,   AVG(buyer_fee_amount::float) AS avg_buyer_fee,   AVG(seller_fee_amount::float) AS avg_seller_fee,   AVG(retail_fee_amount::float) AS avg_retail_fee,   AVG(days_between_transaction_and_event::float) AS avg_days_to_event   /* Timing metrics */,   AVG(days_listing_before_purchase::float) AS avg_days_listed,   AVG(minutes_listing_before_purchase::float) AS avg_minutes_listed,   AVG(listing_price_amount::float) AS avg_listing_price   /* Price metrics */,   AVG(original_listing_price_amount::float) AS avg_original_price,   COUNT(DISTINCT event_type_code) AS distinct_event_types   /* Event statistics */,   COUNT(DISTINCT season_type_code) AS distinct_season_types,   MIN(season_year) AS earliest_season,   MAX(season_year) AS latest_season,   SUM(     CASE       WHEN game_attendance_flag ILIKE '%Y%' THEN 1       ELSE 0     END   ) AS total_attended   /* Attendance and complimentary tickets */,   SUM(     CASE       WHEN total_complimented_flag ILIKE '%Y%' THEN 1       ELSE 0     END   ) AS total_complimentary_tickets,   COUNT(DISTINCT venue_city) AS distinct_cities   /* Venue metrics */,   COUNT(DISTINCT stadium_level_code) AS distinct_stadium_levels,   COUNT(DISTINCT section_name) AS distinct_sections,   MIN(transaction_timestamp) AS earliest_transaction   /* Transaction timing */,   MAX(transaction_timestamp) AS latest_transaction,   MIN(event_start_date) AS earliest_event   /* Event timing */,   MAX(event_start_date) AS latest_event,   COUNT(DISTINCT market_place_code) AS distinct_marketplaces   /* Market metrics */,   COUNT(DISTINCT sale_type_code) AS distinct_sale_types,   COUNT(DISTINCT primary_purchase_type_code) AS distinct_purchase_types,   COUNT(DISTINCT seat_class_code) AS distinct_seat_classes with  stgData as (  SELECT    'HOU' AS clubCode   , 'FanReach' AS sourceSystemName   , NULLIF(USER_ID,'') AS user_id   ,IF( `user_properties`[SAFE_OFFSET(0)].`key`='user_id',`user_properties`[SAFE_OFFSET(0)].value.string_value,null) AS userId   ,IF( `user_properties`[SAFE_OFFSET(0)].`key`='ticketing_id',`user_properties`[SAFE_OFFSET(0)].value.string_value,null) AS ticketingId     ,IF( `user_properties`[SAFE_OFFSET(0)].`key`='push_id', `user_properties`[SAFE_OFFSET(0)].value.string_value,NULL)  AS deviceId   , device.vendor_id AS deviceVendorId   , user_pseudo_id   , CASE     WHEN device.category = 'tablet' AND device.operating_system = 'iOS' THEN 'iPad OS'     ELSE device.operating_system   END AS mobileOS   , '' AS phoneNumber   , CONCAT( substring(event_date,1,4),'-',SUBSTRING(event_date,5,2),'-',SUBSTRING(event_date,7,2)  )  as eventDate   , event_name FROM `houston-texans-17356.analytics_218880207.events_intraday_*`  WHERE 1=1     AND `user_properties`[SAFE_OFFSET(0)].`key`  in ('push_id','user_id','ticketing_id')  ),  transformData as (   SELECT      clubCode AS CLUB_CODE     , CONCAT('FanReach' , COALESCE(       deviceId       , deviceVendorId       , user_pseudo_id     )) as CLUB_RECORD_PK     , 'FanReach' AS SOURCE_SYSTEM_NAME     , COALESCE(       USER_ID       ,userId       ,ticketingId       ) as SOURCE_SYSTEM_ID       , COALESCE(       deviceId       , deviceVendorId       , user_pseudo_id     ) AS DEVICE_ID      , mobileOS AS MOBILE_OPERATING_SYSTEM     , phoneNumber AS PHONE_NUMBER     , DATE(eventDate) AS DAY     , count(*) cnt    FROM stgData   WHERE 1=1                  GROUP BY 1, 2, 3, 4, 5 ,6, 7 ,8     )  SELECT * FROM transformData where not SOURCE_SYSTEM_ID is null
